01:06:19.690 --> 01:06:22.340
but also in terms of orientation

01:06:22.340 --> 01:06:26.030
and becoming familiar
with the community.

01:06:26.030 --> 01:06:33.230
As you can imagine, as a very
isolated forestry based community

01:06:33.230 --> 01:06:36.670
on the very isolated West
Coast of Vancouver Island,

01:06:36.670 --> 01:06:42.520
it can be a big jarring to come
from metropolitan China or Iran

01:06:42.520 --> 01:06:46.160
or Pakistan or India or
a myriad of other places.

01:06:46.160 --> 01:06:50.300
So, this program's very
popular at our center as well.

01:06:50.300 --> 01:06:55.530 position:56%
And I was delighted to meet Tom at
