01:07:23.350 --> 01:07:26.850
and the accessibility to
books whether that be free,

01:07:26.850 --> 01:07:30.410
whether that be lending,
whatever that case is.

01:07:30.410 --> 01:07:33.040
So, a really quick
story before I finish.

01:07:33.040 --> 01:07:35.620
I really don't want
to speak too long.

01:07:35.620 --> 01:07:38.610
Our Little Libraries,
we built 26 of them.

01:07:38.610 --> 01:07:40.910 position:56%
