in alternate formats for the blind

01:30:08.300 --> 01:30:12.830
and severely impaired
Delawareans primarily K-12 students

01:30:12.830 --> 01:30:14.980
that we serve.

01:30:14.980 --> 01:30:19.930
Each request received is unique.

01:30:19.930 --> 01:30:23.590
But there is a common goal and
that is to help the student,

01:30:23.590 --> 01:30:29.300
young or old, to read and learn
with the hope of them wanting more.

01:30:29.300 --> 01:30:30.900
