01:30:37.950 --> 01:30:45.640
Our program began in 1989 with five
members and a part-time proctor

01:30:45.640 --> 01:30:48.010
that focused on producing braille.

01:30:48.010 --> 01:30:51.370 position:56%
And they earned their certifications
in braille transcription

01:30:51.370 --> 01:30:53.930
from the Library of Congress.

01:30:53.930 --> 01:30:56.370
