that the client can read

01:33:18.030 --> 01:33:22.810
and interpret the information
the way the author intended it

01:33:22.810 --> 01:33:24.930
to be read.

01:33:24.930 --> 01:33:29.880
The participants in this program
have always strived for excellence

01:33:29.880 --> 01:33:31.560
