and just put different text in

01:58:38.420 --> 01:58:40.320
and different sign language videos.

01:58:40.320 --> 01:58:42.980
And the students all over the
world can get access to it.

01:58:42.980 --> 01:58:48.120
So, this is our little iDeaf
project that started just

01:58:48.120 --> 01:58:51.280
