02:02:32.230 --> 02:02:36.300
My favorite one here is Wimbo
Wa Matatu The Matatu Song.

02:02:36.300 --> 02:02:38.160
Matatu's are mini buses in Kenya

02:02:38.160 --> 02:02:40.620
that are their public
transportation.

02:02:40.620 --> 02:02:44.380 position:56%
And this is actually a bilingual
book that has a song that goes along

02:02:44.380 --> 02:02:46.250
