probably at the end of 4th grade.

02:13:57.780 --> 02:14:01.080
And the idea of the
Montessori school is

02:14:01.080 --> 02:14:05.930
to give the children the training,
the literacy, the discipline,

02:14:05.930 --> 02:14:08.180
all that they need
in order to be able

02:14:08.180 --> 02:14:11.290
to succeed in the public schools.

02:14:11.290 --> 02:14:12.950
So, it really -- it's working.

02:14:12.950 --> 02:14:14.520
As I said, it's up hill.

02:14:14.520 --> 02:14:16.450
It's very hard work.

02:14:16.450 --> 02:14:18.900
It also entails working
with the families.

02:14:18.900 --> 02:14:24.250
In fact, just last year, two of
