old and we have a long tradition

02:15:01.050 --> 02:15:05.680
of education, education
of children and of adults.

02:15:05.680 --> 02:15:08.170
So, teacher training
is in our blood.

02:15:08.170 --> 02:15:10.670
And our sisters there
have really been working

02:15:10.670 --> 02:15:13.880
at training the Dominican people

02:15:13.880 --> 02:15:18.780
to be effective teachers
in this Batey situation.

02:15:18.780 --> 02:15:24.120 position:56%
So, from a container to a Montessori
school, to teacher education,

02:15:24.120 --> 02:15:28.580
